= Tinymce Filter =

This extension provides a TinyMCE filter for the Radiant CMS. 
It allows you to edit the content of your pages in the TinyMCE editor.

Ispired by http://code.google.com/p/radiant-tinymce-extension/.

== Installation ==

  
  # Download master from git hub using git or tarball download:
  
  http://github.com/ginius/radiant_tinymce_filter/tree/master
  
  
  # Copy tinymce with radiant_tags plugin to your /public directory by invoking

  rake radiant:extensions:tinymce_filter:update

== Settings ==

If you want to change the settings of the editor, you can do this by editing the 'observe_mce.js' file. The 'radiant-tags' plugin is used to protect the Radiant tags from being destroyed by the editor.

